values:
TERMS AND CONDITIONS

No dead buyers. You will be blacklisted without hesitation.

No refunds or exchange.

Cash sale is always preferred than trade.

POSB or OCBC bank transfer only. No concealed cash. Payment must be in by 24 hours upon confirmation, unless otherwise stated.

I  will ensure that parcel is well-packed before mailing.

Do top up $2.25 for registered mail.

Meet ups only at my own convenience.

Trades are welcome, only at the original price I got it for, unless otherwise stated.

Prices are slightly negotiable, but do not try to ask for unreasonable discounts of $5/$10 off. I will not hesitate to blacklist you.

For any enquiries, do email me at narayaisloved@gmail.com and I will reply asap.

Feedback:

20 Positive / 0 Negative

I don't chase for feedbacks. But definitely appreciate it. (:


BLACKLISTERS
